## Gene Details:
- **Gene ID:**	[TraesCS2D02G016400](http://202.194.139.32/cgi-bin/geneDetail.py?search=TraesCS2D02G016400)
- **Gene Symbol:** <u>Sr46</u>
- **Gene Name:** Sr46
- **Genome:** [Chinese_Spring1.0](https://ensembl.gramene.org/Triticum_aestivum/Info/Index)
- **Species:** *Triticum aestivum*

## Functional Descriptions:
   - This gene, hereafter referred to as **Sr46**, encodes a coiled-coil NLR protein that conferred stem rust resistance when expressed as a transgene in the susceptible wheat.
   - **Sr46** promotes stem rust resistance in wheats.
